[
  {
    "startTime": 16.26,
    "endTime": 18.26,
    "text": "I'm here today to share with you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.26,
    "endTime": 20.26,
    "text": "an extraordinary journey -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.26,
    "endTime": 23.26,
    "text": "extraordinarily rewarding journey, actually -"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.26,
    "endTime": 25.26,
    "text": "which brought me into"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.26,
    "endTime": 27.26,
    "text": "training rats"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.26,
    "endTime": 29.26,
    "text": "to save human lives"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.26,
    "endTime": 31.26,
    "text": "by detecting landmines"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.26,
    "endTime": 33.260000000000005,
    "text": "and tuberculosis."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 33.26,
    "endTime": 36.26,
    "text": "As a child, I had two passions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.26,
    "endTime": 39.26,
    "text": "One was a passion for rodents."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.26,
    "endTime": 41.26,
    "text": "I had all kinds of rats,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.26,
    "endTime": 43.26,
    "text": "mice, hamsters,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.26,
    "endTime": 45.26,
    "text": "gerbils, squirrels."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.26,
    "endTime": 48.26,
    "text": "You name it, I bred it, and I sold them to pet shops."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 48.26,
    "endTime": 50.26,
    "text": "(Laughter)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 50.26,
    "endTime": 53.26,
    "text": "I also had a passion for Africa."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.26,
    "endTime": 55.26,
    "text": "Growing up in a multicultural environment,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.26,
    "endTime": 57.26,
    "text": "we had African students in the house,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.26,
    "endTime": 59.26,
    "text": "and I learned about their stories,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.26,
    "endTime": 61.26,
    "text": "so different backgrounds,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.26,
    "endTime": 64.259,
    "text": "dependency on imported know-how,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.26,
    "endTime": 66.26,
    "text": "goods, services,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.26,
    "endTime": 69.26,
    "text": "exuberant cultural diversity."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.26,
    "endTime": 71.26,
    "text": "Africa was truly fascinating for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.26,
    "endTime": 73.26,
    "text": "I became an industrial engineer,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.26,
    "endTime": 75.26,
    "text": "engineer in product development,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.26,
    "endTime": 78.26,
    "text": "and I focused on appropriate detection technologies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 78.26,
    "endTime": 80.26,
    "text": "actually the first appropriate technologies"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 80.26,
    "endTime": 83.26,
    "text": "for developing countries."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.26,
    "endTime": 85.26,
    "text": "I started working in the industry,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.26,
    "endTime": 87.26,
    "text": "but I wasn't really happy to contribute"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.26,
    "endTime": 90.26,
    "text": "to a material consumer society"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.26,
    "endTime": 93.26,
    "text": "in a linear, extracting"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.26,
    "endTime": 95.26,
    "text": "and manufacturing mode."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.26,
    "endTime": 97.26,
    "text": "I quit my job to focus on the real world problem:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.26,
    "endTime": 100.26,
    "text": "landmines."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.26,
    "endTime": 103.26,
    "text": "We're talking '95 now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 103.26,
    "endTime": 106.26,
    "text": "Princess Diana is announcing on TV"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.26,
    "endTime": 108.26,
    "text": "that landmines form a structural barrier"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.26,
    "endTime": 111.26,
    "text": "to any development, which is really true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.26,
    "endTime": 113.26,
    "text": "As long as these devices are there,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.26,
    "endTime": 115.26,
    "text": "or there is suspicion of landmines,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.26,
    "endTime": 117.26,
    "text": "you can't really enter into the land."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.26,
    "endTime": 119.26,
    "text": "Actually, there was an appeal worldwide"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 119.26,
    "endTime": 122.26,
    "text": "for new detectors"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.26,
    "endTime": 124.26,
    "text": "sustainable in the environments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.26,
    "endTime": 126.26,
    "text": "where they're needed to produce,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.26,
    "endTime": 128.25900000000001,
    "text": "which is mainly in the developing world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 128.259,
    "endTime": 130.259,
    "text": "We chose rats."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.259,
    "endTime": 132.26,
    "text": "Why would you choose rats?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.26,
    "endTime": 134.26,
    "text": "Because, aren't they vermin?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.26,
    "endTime": 136.26,
    "text": "Well, actually rats are,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.26,
    "endTime": 138.26,
    "text": "in contrary to what most people think about them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 138.26,
    "endTime": 142.26,
    "text": "rats are highly sociable creatures."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.26,
    "endTime": 145.26,
    "text": "And actually, our product -- what you see here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.26,
    "endTime": 147.26,
    "text": "There's a target somewhere here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.26,
    "endTime": 149.26,
    "text": "You see an operator, a trained African"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.26,
    "endTime": 151.26,
    "text": "with his rats in front"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.26,
    "endTime": 153.26,
    "text": "who actually are left and right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.26,
    "endTime": 155.26,
    "text": "There, the animal finds a mine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.26,
    "endTime": 157.26,
    "text": "It scratches on the soil."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.26,
    "endTime": 160.26,
    "text": "And the animal comes back for a food reward."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.26,
    "endTime": 162.26,
    "text": "Very, very simple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.26,
    "endTime": 165.26,
    "text": "Very sustainable in this environment."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.26,
    "endTime": 168.26,
    "text": "Here, the animal gets its food reward."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.26,
    "endTime": 170.26,
    "text": "And that's how it works."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.26,
    "endTime": 172.26,
    "text": "Very, very simple."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.26,
    "endTime": 174.26,
    "text": "Now why would you use rats?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.26,
    "endTime": 176.26,
    "text": "Rats have been used since the '50s last century,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.26,
    "endTime": 179.26,
    "text": "in all kinds of experiments."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 179.26,
    "endTime": 182.26,
    "text": "Rats have more genetic material"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.26,
    "endTime": 184.26,
    "text": "allocated to olfaction"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.26,
    "endTime": 186.26,
    "text": "than any other mammal species."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.26,
    "endTime": 189.26,
    "text": "They're extremely sensitive to smell."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.26,
    "endTime": 192.26,
    "text": "Moreover, they have the mechanisms to map all these smells"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.26,
    "endTime": 195.26,
    "text": "and to communicate about it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.26,
    "endTime": 197.26,
    "text": "Now how do we communicate with rats?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.26,
    "endTime": 200.26,
    "text": "Well don't talk rat,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.26,
    "endTime": 202.26,
    "text": "but we have a clicker,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 202.26,
    "endTime": 204.26,
    "text": "a standard method for animal training,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 204.26,
    "endTime": 206.26,
    "text": "which you see there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.26,
    "endTime": 209.26,
    "text": "A clicker, which makes a particular sound"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 209.26,
    "endTime": 212.26,
    "text": "with which you can reinforce particular behaviors."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.26,
    "endTime": 215.26,
    "text": "First of all, we associate the click sound with a food reward,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 215.26,
    "endTime": 218.26,
    "text": "which is smashed banana and peanuts together in a syringe."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.26,
    "endTime": 221.26,
    "text": "Once the animal knows click, food,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.26,
    "endTime": 223.26,
    "text": "click, food, click, food --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.26,
    "endTime": 225.26,
    "text": "so click is food --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 225.26,
    "endTime": 227.26,
    "text": "we bring it in a cage with a hole,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.26,
    "endTime": 229.26,
    "text": "and actually the animal learns"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.26,
    "endTime": 231.26,
    "text": "to stick the nose in the hole"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.26,
    "endTime": 233.26,
    "text": "under which a target scent is placed,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.26,
    "endTime": 235.26,
    "text": "and to do that for five seconds --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.26,
    "endTime": 237.26,
    "text": "five seconds, which is long for a rat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.26,
    "endTime": 240.26,
    "text": "Once the animal knows this, we make the task a bit more difficult."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.26,
    "endTime": 243.26,
    "text": "It learns how to find the target smell"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.26,
    "endTime": 246.26,
    "text": "in a cage with several holes, up to 10 holes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 246.26,
    "endTime": 248.26,
    "text": "Then the animal learns"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.26,
    "endTime": 250.26,
    "text": "to walk on a leash in the open"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.26,
    "endTime": 252.26,
    "text": "and find targets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.26,
    "endTime": 255.26,
    "text": "In the next step, animals learn"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.26,
    "endTime": 257.26,
    "text": "to find real mines in real minefields."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.26,
    "endTime": 260.26,
    "text": "They are tested and accredited"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.26,
    "endTime": 262.26,
    "text": "according to International Mine Action Standards,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.26,
    "endTime": 265.26,
    "text": "just like dogs have to pass a test."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.26,
    "endTime": 267.26,
    "text": "This consists of 400 square meters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.26,
    "endTime": 270.26,
    "text": "There's a number of mines"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 270.26,
    "endTime": 272.26,
    "text": "placed blindly,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.26,
    "endTime": 275.26,
    "text": "and the team of trainer and their rat"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 275.26,
    "endTime": 278.26,
    "text": "have to find all the targets."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.26,
    "endTime": 282.26,
    "text": "If the animal does that, it gets a license"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.26,
    "endTime": 284.26,
    "text": "as an accredited animal"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.26,
    "endTime": 286.26,
    "text": "to be operational in the field --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.26,
    "endTime": 288.26,
    "text": "just like dogs, by the way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 288.26,
    "endTime": 290.26,
    "text": "Maybe one slight difference:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.26,
    "endTime": 293.26,
    "text": "we can train rats at a fifth of the price"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.26,
    "endTime": 295.26,
    "text": "of training the mining dog."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.26,
    "endTime": 297.26,
    "text": "This is our team in Mozambique:"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.26,
    "endTime": 299.26,
    "text": "one Tanzanian trainer,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.26,
    "endTime": 301.26,
    "text": "who transfers the skills"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.26,
    "endTime": 303.26,
    "text": "to these three Mozambican fellows."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 303.26,
    "endTime": 306.26,
    "text": "And you should see the pride in the eyes of these people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 306.26,
    "endTime": 308.26,
    "text": "They have a skill,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.26,
    "endTime": 310.26,
    "text": "which makes them much less dependent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.26,
    "endTime": 312.26,
    "text": "on foreign aid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.26,
    "endTime": 315.26,
    "text": "Moreover, this small team"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.26,
    "endTime": 318.26,
    "text": "together with, of course, you need the heavy vehicles"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.26,
    "endTime": 321.26,
    "text": "and the manual de-miners to follow-up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.26,
    "endTime": 324.26,
    "text": "But with this small investment in a rat capacity,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 324.26,
    "endTime": 327.26,
    "text": "we have demonstrated in Mozambique"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.26,
    "endTime": 330.26,
    "text": "that we can reduce the cost-price per square meter"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.26,
    "endTime": 332.26,
    "text": "up to 60 percent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.26,
    "endTime": 334.26,
    "text": "of what is currently normal --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 334.26,
    "endTime": 336.26,
    "text": "two dollars per square meter, we do it at $1.18,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.26,
    "endTime": 338.26,
    "text": "and we can still bring that price down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.26,
    "endTime": 340.26,
    "text": "Question of scale."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.26,
    "endTime": 342.26,
    "text": "If you can bring in more rats,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.26,
    "endTime": 344.26,
    "text": "we can actually make the output even bigger."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 344.26,
    "endTime": 347.26,
    "text": "We have a demonstration site in Mozambique."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 347.26,
    "endTime": 350.26,
    "text": "Eleven African governments"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.26,
    "endTime": 353.26,
    "text": "have seen that they can become less dependent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.26,
    "endTime": 355.26,
    "text": "by using this technology."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.26,
    "endTime": 357.26,
    "text": "They have signed the pact for peace"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.26,
    "endTime": 360.26,
    "text": "and treaty in the Great Lakes region,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.26,
    "endTime": 363.26,
    "text": "and they endorse hero rats"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 363.26,
    "endTime": 366.26,
    "text": "to clear their common borders of landmines."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 366.26,
    "endTime": 369.26,
    "text": "But let me bring you to a very different problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.26,
    "endTime": 371.26,
    "text": "And there's about 6,000 people last year"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.26,
    "endTime": 373.26,
    "text": "that walked on a landmine,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 373.26,
    "endTime": 375.26,
    "text": "but worldwide last year,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 375.26,
    "endTime": 377.26,
    "text": "almost 1.9 million died from tuberculosis"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 377.26,
    "endTime": 380.26,
    "text": "as a first cause of infection."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.26,
    "endTime": 383.26,
    "text": "Especially in Africa"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.26,
    "endTime": 386.26,
    "text": "where T.B. and HIV are strongly linked,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.26,
    "endTime": 390.26,
    "text": "there is a huge common problem."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.26,
    "endTime": 394.26,
    "text": "Microscopy, the standard WHO procedure,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 394.26,
    "endTime": 397.26,
    "text": "reaches from 40 to 60 percent reliability."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.26,
    "endTime": 401.26,
    "text": "In Tanzania -- the numbers don't lie --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.26,
    "endTime": 404.26,
    "text": "45 percent of people -- T.B. patients --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.26,
    "endTime": 407.26,
    "text": "get diagnosed with T.B. before they die."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.26,
    "endTime": 411.26,
    "text": "It means that, if you have T.B.,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 411.26,
    "endTime": 413.26,
    "text": "you have more chance that you won't be detected,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 413.26,
    "endTime": 416.26,
    "text": "but will just die from T.B. secondary infections and so on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.26,
    "endTime": 422.26,
    "text": "And if, however,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 422.26,
    "endTime": 424.26,
    "text": "you are detected very early, diagnosed early,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 424.26,
    "endTime": 426.26,
    "text": "treatment can start,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 426.26,
    "endTime": 429.26,
    "text": "and even in HIV-positives, it makes sense."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 429.26,
    "endTime": 431.26,
    "text": "You can actually cure T.B.,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.26,
    "endTime": 434.26,
    "text": "even in HIV-positives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434.26,
    "endTime": 437.26,
    "text": "So in our common language, Dutch,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 437.26,
    "endTime": 439.26,
    "text": "the name for T.B."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 439.26,
    "endTime": 441.26,
    "text": "is \"tering,\""
  },
  {
    "startTime": 441.26,
    "endTime": 443.26,
    "text": "which, etymologically,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 443.26,
    "endTime": 446.26,
    "text": "refers to the smell of tar."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.26,
    "endTime": 448.26,
    "text": "Already the old Chinese"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 448.26,
    "endTime": 451.26,
    "text": "and the Greek, Hippocrates,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.26,
    "endTime": 453.26,
    "text": "have actually published,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 453.26,
    "endTime": 456.26,
    "text": "documented, that T.B. can be diagnosed"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 456.26,
    "endTime": 458.26,
    "text": "based on the volatiles"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 458.26,
    "endTime": 461.26,
    "text": "exuding from patients."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.26,
    "endTime": 463.26,
    "text": "So what we did is we collected some samples --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.26,
    "endTime": 465.26,
    "text": "just as a way of testing --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 465.26,
    "endTime": 467.26,
    "text": "from hospitals,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 467.26,
    "endTime": 470.26,
    "text": "trained rats on them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 470.26,
    "endTime": 472.26,
    "text": "and see if this works,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 472.26,
    "endTime": 474.26,
    "text": "and wonder, well,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 474.26,
    "endTime": 476.26,
    "text": "we can reach 89 percent sensitivity,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 476.26,
    "endTime": 478.26,
    "text": "86 percent specificity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 478.26,
    "endTime": 480.26,
    "text": "using multiple rats in a row."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 480.26,
    "endTime": 482.26,
    "text": "This is how it works,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 483.26,
    "endTime": 486.26,
    "text": "and really, this is a generic technology."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 486.26,
    "endTime": 489.26,
    "text": "We're talking now explosives, tuberculosis,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 489.26,
    "endTime": 491.26,
    "text": "but can you imagine,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 491.26,
    "endTime": 493.26,
    "text": "you can actually put anything under there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 493.26,
    "endTime": 495.26,
    "text": "So how does it work?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 495.26,
    "endTime": 497.26,
    "text": "You have a cassette with 10 samples."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 497.26,
    "endTime": 500.26,
    "text": "You put these 10 samples at once in the cage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 500.26,
    "endTime": 502.26,
    "text": "An animal only needs two hundredths of a second"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 502.26,
    "endTime": 505.26,
    "text": "to discriminate the scent, so it goes extremely fast."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 505.26,
    "endTime": 508.26,
    "text": "Here it's already at the third sample."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 508.26,
    "endTime": 511.26,
    "text": "This is a positive sample."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 512.26,
    "endTime": 515.26,
    "text": "It gets a click sound and comes for the food reward."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 517.26,
    "endTime": 519.26,
    "text": "And by doing so, very fast,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 519.26,
    "endTime": 522.26,
    "text": "we can have like a second-line opinion"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 522.26,
    "endTime": 524.26,
    "text": "to see which patients are positive,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 524.26,
    "endTime": 527.26,
    "text": "which are negative."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 527.26,
    "endTime": 529.26,
    "text": "Just as an indication,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 529.26,
    "endTime": 531.26,
    "text": "whereas a microscopist can process"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 531.26,
    "endTime": 533.26,
    "text": "40 samples in a day,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 533.26,
    "endTime": 535.26,
    "text": "a rat can process"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 535.26,
    "endTime": 537.26,
    "text": "the same amount of samples"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 537.26,
    "endTime": 539.26,
    "text": "in seven minutes only."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 539.26,
    "endTime": 541.26,
    "text": "A cage like this --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 541.26,
    "endTime": 546.26,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 546.26,
    "endTime": 549.26,
    "text": "A cage like this -- provided that you have rats,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 549.26,
    "endTime": 551.26,
    "text": "and we have now currently"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 551.26,
    "endTime": 553.26,
    "text": "25 tuberculosis rats --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 553.26,
    "endTime": 556.26,
    "text": "a cage like this, operating throughout the day,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 556.26,
    "endTime": 559.26,
    "text": "can process 1,680 samples."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 561.26,
    "endTime": 564.26,
    "text": "Can you imagine the potential offspring applications --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 564.26,
    "endTime": 566.26,
    "text": "environmental detection"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 566.26,
    "endTime": 568.26,
    "text": "of pollutants in soils,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 568.26,
    "endTime": 570.26,
    "text": "customs applications,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 570.26,
    "endTime": 573.26,
    "text": "detection of illicit goods in containers and so on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 574.26,
    "endTime": 576.26,
    "text": "But let's stick first to tuberculosis."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 576.26,
    "endTime": 578.26,
    "text": "I just want to briefly highlight,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 578.26,
    "endTime": 580.26,
    "text": "the blue rods"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 580.26,
    "endTime": 582.26,
    "text": "are the scores of microscopy only"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 582.26,
    "endTime": 585.26,
    "text": "at the five clinics in Dar es Salaam"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 585.26,
    "endTime": 587.26,
    "text": "on a population of 500,000 people,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 587.26,
    "endTime": 590.26,
    "text": "where 15,000 reported to get a test done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 590.26,
    "endTime": 593.26,
    "text": "Microscopy for 1,800 patients."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 593.26,
    "endTime": 597.26,
    "text": "And by just presenting the samples once more to the rats"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 597.26,
    "endTime": 600.26,
    "text": "and looping those results back,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 600.26,
    "endTime": 602.26,
    "text": "we were able to increase case detection rates"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 602.26,
    "endTime": 604.26,
    "text": "by over 30 percent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 604.26,
    "endTime": 606.26,
    "text": "Throughout last year,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 606.26,
    "endTime": 608.26,
    "text": "we've been -- depending on which intervals you take --"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 608.26,
    "endTime": 610.26,
    "text": "we've been consistently"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 610.26,
    "endTime": 612.26,
    "text": "increasing case detection rates"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 612.26,
    "endTime": 614.26,
    "text": "in five hospitals in Dar es Salaam"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 614.26,
    "endTime": 617.26,
    "text": "between 30 and 40 percent."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 617.26,
    "endTime": 619.26,
    "text": "So this is really considerable."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 619.26,
    "endTime": 621.26,
    "text": "Knowing that a missed patient by microscopy"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 621.26,
    "endTime": 623.26,
    "text": "infects up to 15 people,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 623.26,
    "endTime": 625.26,
    "text": "healthy people, per year,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 625.26,
    "endTime": 627.26,
    "text": "you can be sure"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 627.26,
    "endTime": 629.26,
    "text": "that we have saved lots of lives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 629.26,
    "endTime": 632.26,
    "text": "At least our hero rats have saved lots of lives."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 632.26,
    "endTime": 634.26,
    "text": "The way forward for us"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 634.26,
    "endTime": 636.26,
    "text": "is now to standardize this technology."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 636.26,
    "endTime": 638.26,
    "text": "And there are simple things"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 638.26,
    "endTime": 642.26,
    "text": "like, for instance, we have a small laser in the sniffer hole"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 642.26,
    "endTime": 644.26,
    "text": "where the animal has to stick for five seconds."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 644.26,
    "endTime": 646.26,
    "text": "So, to standardize this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 646.26,
    "endTime": 648.26,
    "text": "Also, to standardize the pellets,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 648.26,
    "endTime": 650.26,
    "text": "the food rewards,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 650.26,
    "endTime": 652.26,
    "text": "and to semi-automate this"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 652.26,
    "endTime": 655.26,
    "text": "in order to replicate this on a much larger scale"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 655.26,
    "endTime": 658.26,
    "text": "and affect the lives of many more people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 658.26,
    "endTime": 661.26,
    "text": "To conclude, there are also other applications at the horizon."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 661.26,
    "endTime": 663.26,
    "text": "Here is a first prototype"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 663.26,
    "endTime": 665.26,
    "text": "of our camera rat,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 665.26,
    "endTime": 667.26,
    "text": "which is a rat with a rat backpack"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 667.26,
    "endTime": 669.26,
    "text": "with a camera that can go under rubble"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 669.26,
    "endTime": 671.26,
    "text": "to detect for victims"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 671.26,
    "endTime": 673.26,
    "text": "after earthquake and so on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 673.26,
    "endTime": 675.26,
    "text": "This is in a prototype stage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 675.26,
    "endTime": 677.26,
    "text": "We don't have a working system here yet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 678.26,
    "endTime": 681.26,
    "text": "To conclude, I would actually like to say,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 681.26,
    "endTime": 683.26,
    "text": "you may think this is about rats, these projects,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 683.26,
    "endTime": 685.26,
    "text": "but in the end it is about people."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 685.26,
    "endTime": 687.26,
    "text": "It is about empowering vulnerable communities"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 687.26,
    "endTime": 690.26,
    "text": "to tackle difficult, expensive"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 690.26,
    "endTime": 693.26,
    "text": "and dangerous humanitarian detection tasks,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 693.26,
    "endTime": 696.26,
    "text": "and doing that with a local resource,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 696.26,
    "endTime": 698.26,
    "text": "plenty available."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 698.26,
    "endTime": 701.26,
    "text": "So something completely different"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 701.26,
    "endTime": 704.26,
    "text": "is to keep on challenging your perception"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 704.26,
    "endTime": 707.26,
    "text": "about the resources surrounding you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 707.26,
    "endTime": 710.26,
    "text": "whether they are environmental,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 710.26,
    "endTime": 713.26,
    "text": "technological, animal, or human."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 715.26,
    "endTime": 718.26,
    "text": "And to respectfully harmonize with them"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 718.26,
    "endTime": 721.26,
    "text": "in order to foster a sustainable world."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 721.26,
    "endTime": 723.26,
    "text": "Thank you very much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 723.26,
    "endTime": 725.26,
    "text": "(Applause)"
  }
]